OL,3,CCharities warn of 'devastating' effect
OL,4,Cof wildfires on nature
OL,6,FEcosystems have been "decimated", a
OL,7,Fcharity as warned, as the number of
OL,8,Fwildfires in Wales has dramatically
OL,9,Fincreased.
OL,11,FThe combination of one of the driest
OL,12,FMarches in decades and warmer than
OL,13,Faverage temperatures in April has led
OL,14,Fto the UK being hit by one of the
OL,15,Fworst fire seasons on record.
OL,17,FThe number of wildfires in Wales has
OL,18,Frisen dramatically this year. Fire
OL,19,Fservices across the country said they
OL,20,Fwere under pressure last week after
OL,21,Fweeks of wildfires.
