OL,6,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue service
OL,7,Fresponded to 34 wildfire callouts
OL,8,Fbetween 1 January and 10 April in
OL,9,F2024, but 445 over the same period in
OL,10,F2025 ` a 1,200% increase.
OL,12,FThe three fire services in Wales have
OL,13,Freported responding to over 1,300
OL,14,Fgrass fires this year.
OL,16,FAbergwesyn Common in Powys was
OL,17,Fconsumed by a 1,600 hectare fire ` an
OL,18,Farea roughly 400 times the size of
OL,19,FCardiff's Principality Stadium.
