OL,3,CCharities warn of 'devastating' effect
OL,4,Cof wildfires on nature
OL,6,FNational Trust rangers fear that the
OL,7,Fbreeding habitat of the area's last
OL,8,Fknown population of golden plovers, a
OL,9,Frare, protected bird found in upland
OL,10,Fmoorlands, will have been lost.
OL,12,FChris Smith, the National Trust's
OL,13,Fcountryside manager for Mid and South
OL,14,FWales, said: "The sheer scale of the
OL,15,Ffire on Abergwesyn Common is hard to
OL,16,Ffathom.
