OL,3,CCharities warn of 'devastating' effect
OL,4,Cof wildfires on nature
OL,6,F"As a Site of Special Scientific
OL,7,FInterest, the impacts on wildlife are
OL,8,Fwidespread, with birds' nests,
OL,9,Finsects, amphibians and reptiles all
OL,10,Fscorched by fire. Whole ecosystems
OL,11,Fhave been decimated and will remain
OL,12,Faltered well into the future.
OL,14,F"Alongside this, the huge loss of
OL,15,Fsurface vegetation leaves the peat
OL,16,Fbogs we have been working hard to
OL,17,Frestore and rewet vulnerable to
OL,18,Ferosion and at further risk of fire
OL,19,Fand carbon loss.
