OL,3,CCharities warn of 'devastating' effect
OL,4,Cof wildfires on nature
OL,6,F"Where the flames burnt down to the
OL,7,Fpeat soils, they will take hundreds of
OL,8,Fyears to recover."
OL,10,FWWF Cymru said the "devastating"
OL,11,Fwildfires are a "stark reminder that
OL,12,Fthe climate and nature crisis is upon
OL,13,Fus".
OL,15,FGareth Clubb, director at WWF Cymru,
OL,16,Fsaid: "With one in six assessed
OL,17,Fspecies at risk of extinction in Wales
OL,18,Falready, these wildfires are having a
OL,19,Fdevastating effect on wildlife and
OL,20,Fnature.
